import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Header, Container, Callout } from '../components/blocks'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<Header sx={{ bg: 'coolBg', mb: 0 }} width="narrow">
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components}>{`Register`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components}>{`Your ticket is free, including meals & swag. See you in November!`}</MDXTag>
<Callout sx={{ px: 0, py: 0, mt: [3, 4], mb: 0, maxWidth: '95vw' }}>
  <iframe
    className="airtable-embed"
    src="https://airtable.com/embed/shrLdJGnv7CzhSsn1?backgroundColor=yellow"
    frameBorder="0"
    onMouseWheel=""
    width="100%"
    height={768}
    style={{ background: 'transparent', maxWidth: '100%' }}
  />
</Callout>
</Header></MDXTag>
